hadiths[68]{hadithnumber,text}:
735,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna : jisney masjid ki taamir ki, jis mein Allah ka zikr kiya jata hai, Allah Taala uskey liye jannat mein ghar tayyar kerega."
736,"Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney Allah (ki raza hasil kerney) key liye masjid taamir ki, Allah uskey liye jannat mein wesa hi (ghar) tayyar kerega."
737,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney apney maal sey Allah key liye masjid taamir ki, Allah Taala uskey liye jannat mein ghar tayyar kerega."
738,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney Allah key liye qataat key ghosle jitni ya us sey bhi chhoti masjid banai, Allah Taala uskey liye jannat mein ghar tayyar kerega."
739,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat nahin aayegi, yahan tak key log masjidon mein fakhr karney lagengey."
740,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main dekhta hun (mujhey yaqin hai) ke tum log merey baad is tarah oonchi oonchi masjiden banaogey, jis tarah yahudiyon ney apney ibadat khaney aur esaiyon ney apney girjey unchey unchey banaey."
741,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis qom key aamaal kharab ho jatey hain, wo masjidon ki sajawat karney lagti hai."
742,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Masjide Nabawi ki jagah (masjid banney sey pehley) banu Najaar ki milkiyat thi. wahan khajoor key kuchh darkht aur mushrikon ki chand qabren thin. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : mujh sey is zamin ka soda kar lo. unhoney kaha : hum to iski qeemat hergiz nahin leingey (is jagah ko masjid key liye waqf kar diya). chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney taamir shuru kar di aur Sahaba kiram aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko gaara mitti detey jatey they aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey they : asal zindagi to aakhirat ki zindagi hai. aey Allah ! ansaar aur muhajrin ki maghfirat farma dey. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : masjid ki taamir sey pehley Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jahan namaz ka waqt ho jata, wahin namaz padh letey they."
743,"Hazrat Usman bin Abi Al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen Taaif mein us jagah masjid bananey ka hukm diya, jahan unka but huwa karta tha."
744,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke un sey un baaghon key barey mein sawal kiya gaya, jin mein najaasat (khaad key tor par) dali jati hai, to unhoney farmaya : jab unhen kaee baar pani dey diya jaey to (uskey baad) un mein namaz padh lo. unhoney ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf mansub ki hai."
745,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qabristaan aur ghusl-khaney key siwa sari zamin masjid hai."
746,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney saat jagahon mein namaz padhney sey mana farmaya : kuda karkat phainkney ki jagah, (janwer zibeh karney ki jagah) mein, qabristaan mein, aam raastey mein, ghusl khaney mein, oonton key baadey mein, aur Kaba shareef key ooper (chhat par)."
747,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : saat jagah namaz padhna jayez nahin. Baitullah ki chhat par, qabristaan mein, kuda karkat phainkney ki jagah mein, janwer zibeh karney ki jagah mein , ghusl khaney mein, oonton key baadey mein, aur aam raastey key darmiyan mein."
748,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo kaam masjid mein karney munasib nahin, wo ye hain : usey raah guzar na banaya jaey, is mein kisi hathiyar ki numaish na ki jaey, kamaan na pakdi jaey, (tarkash sey) teer na nikaley jaeyn, us main kachchaa gosht na ley jaya jaey, (mujrim par) had na lagai jaey, kisi sey qisaas na liya jaey aur usey bazar na banaya jaey (kharid aur farokht na ki jaey)."
749,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid (Hazrat Shuaib bin Muhammad (Rahimahullah) sey , aur wo apney dada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma)) sey riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney masjid mein kharid aur farokht aur she'r goi sey mana farmaya."
750,"Hazrat Waasila Isqaa' (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apni masjidon ko bachchon, deewanon, bad khaslat logon, kharid aur farokht, jhagdon, shor-ghul, haden laganey aur talwaarein khinchney sey door rakho, aur in key darwazon key qarib istinja aur wuzu ki jagah banao, aur Jume key din in mein khushbu (agarbatti waghera) sulgaao."
751,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamanae Mubarak mein masjid mein so jaya kartey they."
752,"Hazrat Yaeesh bin Qais bin Tikhfaa apney walid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain, wo as-haabe suffa mein sey they, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hum sey farmaya : aao chalen. hum Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) key ghar ki taraf rawana huye (wahan ja kar) hamney khaya piya. (uskey baad) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hum sey farmaya : chaho to yahan so jaao, chaho to masjid mein chaley jaao. hamney arz kiya : hum to masjid mein hi chaley jaaeyngey."
753,"Hazrat Abu-Zar Ghifaari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! sab sey pehley kon si masjid banai gaee? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Masjide Haram. mainey kaha : phir kon si? farmaya : phir Masjide Aqsaa. mainey kaha : unkey darmiyan kitni muddat ka farq hai? farmaya : chaalis saal. phir sari zamin terey liye namaz ki jagah hai jahan waqt aa jaey, wahin namaz padh ley."
754,"Hazrat Mehmood bin Rabee Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, ye wo Sahaba hain jinkey ghar mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney dol sey pani ley kar unkey kunein mein kulli farmaai thi, unhoney Hazrat Utban bin Malik Saalimi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki, jo apney qabiley banu Salim (ki masjid mein un) key Imam they, unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath jange Badr mein bhi shirkat farmaai thi. unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! meri nazar kamzor ho gaee hai, aur sailab aata hai to main apney qabiley ki masjid tak nahin pahunch sakta. wahan sey guzarnaa merey liye mushkil ho jata hai. agar aap munasib samjhen to merey yahaan tashrif la kar merey ghar main eik jagah namaz ada farmaeyn, aur main wahan namaz padha karun. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (achchha) main aaunga. jab din kafi chadh aaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif ley aaye. aap ney (andar aaney ki) ijazat talab farmaai, mainey ijazat dey di. aap bethey nahin, pehley farmaya : tum apney ghar mein kis jagah chahtey ho ke main wahan namaz padhun? mainey us jagah ki taraf ishara kar diya jahan main namaz padhna chahta tha (aur wo jagah is maqsad key liye makhsus ki thi). Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho gaey. hamney aap key peechhey saf bana li to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein do rakat namaz padha di. phir mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khana khilaney key liye rok liya jo abhi tayyar ho raha tha."
755,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik Ansari Sahaba ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pegham bheja ke merey ghar tashrif la kar merey liye ghar main eik masjid (namaz ki jagah) muqarrar kar dijiye jahan main namaz padha karun. us waqt wo Sahaba na-bina ho chukey they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur us Sahaba ki farmaaish puri ki.
756,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : merey eik chacha jaan ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye khana tayyar kiya. unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey arz kiya : meri khahish hai ke aap merey ghar tashrif la kar khana tanaawul (khaaey) farmaain aur namaz bhi ada farmaeyn, chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley aaye. ghar main eik purani chataai thi, unhoney uskey eik hissey ko saaf kara key is par pani chhidakwaa diya (taake naram ho jaey). Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (khajoor key patton ki bani hui is chataai par) namaz ada farmaai aur hamney bhi aap ki iqtida (pairvi) mein namaz padhi. Imam Abu-Adbullah Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya ke (riwayat mein mazkur) ""فحل"" sey murad aisi chataai hai jo (kasrate istimal ki wajeh sey) siyah ho chuki ho."
757,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney masjid sey kuda karkat nikala, Allah uskey liye jannat mein ghar taamir kerega."
758,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hukm diya ke mahlon mein masjiden taamir ki jaeyn, unhen paak saaf rakha jaey aur unhen khushbu lagai jaey."
759,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mahlon mein masjiden bananey, unhen pak rakhney aur unhen khushbu laganey ka hukm diya hai."
760,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : sab sey pehley jisney masjidon mein chiragh roshan kiye, wo Hazrat Tameem daari (Raziallahu anhu) hain."
761,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera aur Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko masjid ki deewar par balgham nazar aaya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik kankari ley kar usey khurch diya, phir farmaya : koi shakhs jab balgham thooknaa chahey, to samney na thookey, na daain thookey, usey chahiye ke baain taraf thookey ya apney baain paon key nichey thook ley."
762,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko masjid mein qibley ki taraf (deewar par) balgham nazar aaya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is qadr ghazab naak huye ke Chehra Mubarak surkh ho gaya. (ye dekh kar) eik Ansari khatoon ney aa kar usey khurch diya aur us jagah khushbu laga di. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bahut khub !
763,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) logon ko namaz padha rahey they ke masjid mein qibley ki taraf (deewar par) balgham nazar aaya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey khurch diya. namaz sey farigh ho kar farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi shakhs namaz padh raha hota hai to Allah uskey chehrey ki taraf hota hai, lihaza kisi ko namaz key doran mein samney ki taraf nahin thooknaa chahiye."
764,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney masjid mein qibley ki deewar par laga huwa thook khurch diya.
765,"Hazrat Barida bin Haseeb (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney namaz ada farmaai : (namaz key baad) eik aadmi bola : mujhey kon surkh oont ki ittilaa dega? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tujhey wo (oont) na miley. masjiden to jis kaam key liye bani hain, usi key liye hi bani hain."
766,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney gumshuda chiz ka aelan masjid mein karney sey mana farmaya hai."
767,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka ye irshad suna : jo shakhs kisi ko gumshuda chiz ka masjid mein aelan kartey suney, usey chahiye ke kahey : Allah karey wo chiz tujhey na miley kyonkey masjiden isliye nahin banai gaeen."
768,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar tumhen oonton aur bakriyon key baadey key siwa koi jagah na miley, to bakriyon key baadey mein namaz padh lo, oonton key baadey mein na padho."
769,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bakriyon key baadey mein namaz padh liya karo aur oonton key baadey mein namaz na padho, kyonkey wo shetanon sey paida huye hain."
770,"Hazrat Sabra bin Maabad Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : oonton key baadon mein namaz na padhi jaey, bakriyon key baadey mein padh li jaey."
771,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki beti Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab masjid mein dakhil hotey they to farmatey they : (بِسْمِ اللَّهِ وَالسَّلاَمُ عَلَى رَسُولِ اللَّهِ اللَّهُمَّ اغْفِرْ لِى ذُنُوبِى وَافْتَحْ لِى أَبْوَابَ رَحْمَتِكَ), ''Allah key naam sey dakhil hota hun, aur Allah key Rasool par salam ho, aey Allah ! merey gunah bakhsh dey aur merey liye apni rehmat key darwazey khol dey.'' aur jab (masjid sey) bahar tashrif latey to farmatey they : (بِسْمِ اللَّهِ وَالسَّلاَمُ عَلَى رَسُولِ اللَّهِ اللَّهُمَّ اغْفِرْ لِى ذُنُوبِى وَافْتَحْ لِى أَبْوَابَ فَضْلِكَ), ''Allah key naam sey bahar nikalta hun aur Allah key Rasool par salam ho, aey Allah ! merey gunah bakhsh dey aur merey liye apney Fazal key darwazey khol dey.''"
772,"Hazrat Abu-Humed Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi shakhs masjid mein dakhil ho to usey chahiye ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par salam bhejey, phir kahey : (اللَّهُمَّ وَافْتَحْ لِى أَبْوَابَ رَحْمَتِكَ), ''aey Allah ! merey liye apni rehmat key darwazey khol dey.'' aur jab bahar nikley to kahey : (اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّى أَسْأَلُكَ مِنْ فَضْلِكَ), ''aey Allah ! main tujh sey tera Fazal maangta hun.''"
773,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs jab masjid mein dakhil ho to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par salam bhejey aur kahey : (اللَّهُمَّ وَافْتَحْ لِى أَبْوَابَ رَحْمَتِكَ), ''aey Allah ! merey liye apni rehmat key darwazey khol dey.''aur jab bahar nikley to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par salam bhejey aur kahey : (اللَّهُمَّ اعْصِمْنِى مِنَ الشَّيْطَانِ الرَّجِيمِ), ''aey Allah ! mujhey mardud shetan sey mehfooz rakh.''"
774,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi shakhs wuzu karta hai, aur wuzu bhi khub sanwaar kar karta hai, phir masjid ki taraf aata hai, to sirf namaz key liye (ghar sey) nikalta hai, namaz key siwa aur koi maqsad nahin hota, to wo jo qadam bhi uthata hai, uskey badley Allah Taala uska eik darja buland farmata hai, aur eik gunah maaf karta hai. (us ko isi tarah sawab milta rehta hai) yahan tak key wo masjid mein dakhil ho jata hai, phir jab wo masjid mein dakhil ho jata hai to jab tak wo namaz ki wajeh sey rukaa rehta hai (sawab key lihaz sey) namaz hi mein (shumar) hota hai."
775,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab namaz ki iqaamat ho jaey to namaz key liye daud kar na aao balke (mamool key mutabiq munasib raftaar sey) itminan sey chaltey huye aao, phir jitni namaz (jamaat key sath) mil jaey padh lo, aur jo chhoot jaey wo (baad mein) puri kar lo."
776,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya main tumhen wo amal na bataun jin sey Allah Taala gunah maaf kar deta hai, aur nekiyon mein izafa farma deta hai? Sahaba ney arz kiya : ji haan, Allah key Rasool ! (farma dijiye) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is waqt wuzu pura (sanwaar kar) karna, jab dil na chahta ho aur masjidon ki taraf ziyada qadam uthana aur (eik) namaz key baad (doosri) namaz ka intizar karna."
777,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jis ko ye baat pasand hai ke wo Allah Taala ko kal Islam ki haalat mein miley , usey chahiye ke wo pabandi sey paanchon namazein wahan ada kiya karey jahan un ki Azan hoti hai (masaajid mein jamaat key sath). isliye ke wo hidayat waley kamon mein sey hain, aur Allah Taala ney tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye hidayat key kaam muqarrar kiye hain. meri zindagi ki qism ! agar tum sab gharon mein namaz padhney lago to apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat chhod bethogey aur agar tum ney apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat chhod di to yaqinan gumrah ho jaogey. mainey dekha hai ke hum logon ki ye haalat thi ke namaz ba-jamaat sey sirf wohi munafiq peechhey rehta tha, jiskaa nifaq (sab ko) malum hota tha. aur mainey dekha hai ke (bimar) aadmi ko do aadmiyon key saharey sey laya jata tha yahan tak key wo saf mein shamil ho jata. aur jo shakhs wuzu karta hai aur wuzu achchhi tarah bana sanwaar kar karta hai, phir masjid ki taraf rawana hota hai aur is mein (pahunch kar) namaz padhta hai to wo jo qadam bhi tey karta hai uski wajeh sey Allah Taala uska eik darja buland farmata hai aur eik ghalati maaf farmata hai."
778,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs namaz key liye ghar sey nikla aur ye dua padhi , Allah Taala apney Chehrey Mubarak sey uski taraf tawajjoh farmata hai aur sattar hazar farishtey uskey haq mein bakhshish ki dua kartey hain. (dua ye hai) : (اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّى أَسْأَلُكَ بِحَقِّ السَّائِلِينَ عَلَيْكَ وَأَسْأَلُكَ بِحَقِّ مَمْشَاىَ هَذَا فَإِنِّى لَمْ أَخْرُجْ أَشَرًا وَلاَ بَطَرًا وَلاَ رِيَاءً وَلاَ سُمْعَةً وَخَرَجْتُ اتِّقَاءَ سُخْطِكَ وَابْتِغَاءَ مَرْضَاتِكَ فَأَسْأَلُكَ أَنْ تُعِيذَنِى مِنَ النَّارِ وَأَنْ تَغْفِرَ لِى ذُنُوبِى إِنَّهُ لاَ يَغْفِرُ الذُّنُوبَ إِلاَّ أَنْتَ), ''aey Allah ! main tujh sey sawal karta hun, maangney walon key tujh par haq ki wajeh sey aur main (namaz key liye) apney us chalney key wasile sey tujh sey sawal karta hun, main na fakhr kartey huye nikla hun, na itratey huye, na riyaakaari key liye, na shohrat key liye, main to teri narazi sey bachney key liye, aur teri raza key husool key liye nikla hun, main tujh sey sawal karta hun ke mujhey jahannam sey panah dey dey, aur merey gunah maaf farma dey, terey siwa gunahon ko yaqinan koi nahin bakhsh sakta.''"
779,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah ney farmaya : andheron mein masjidon ki taraf ziyada chal kar janey waley hi Allah ki rehmat mein ghota zan hotey hain."
780,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : andheron mein (masjidon ki taraf) ba-kasrat chalney walon key liye qiyamat key din mukammal Noor ki khushkhabri hai."
781,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : andheron mein masjidon ki taraf ziyada chalney walon ko qiyamat key din mukammal Noor key husool ki khushkhabri dey do."
782,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo masjid sey ziyada door ho, phir jo us sey bhi ziyada door ho, to uska sawab pehley shakhs sey bhi ziyada hai."
783,"Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik Ansari Sahaba ka ghar Madiney mein sab sey door tha. (iskey bawajood) uski koi namaz Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath (baa-jamaa't) ada honey sey nahin rehti thi. Hazrat Abi (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mujhey is par taras aaya, mainey kaha : falan sahab ! agar aap eik gadhaa kharid lein to (raastey mein) ret ki garmi bardasht karney sey, aur patharon sey thokar lag janey sey mehfooz rahen, aur zamin key keedey makodon (saanp, bichchhu waghera) sey bhi bach jaeyn. usney kaha : qism hai Allah ki ! mujhey to ye baat pasand nahin ke mera ghar Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ghar sey mila huwa ho. uskey ye alfaz mujhey bahut giraan mehsus huye yahan tak key mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key dare-aqdas par hazir ho kar ye baat arz kar di. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney usey talab farma kar daryaft farmaya to usney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key samney bhi wohi baat keh di. aur kaha ke usey apney qadmon key nishaanaat par sawab ki ummid hai. tab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tu ney jis sawab ki niyat ki hai, wo tujhey mil jaeyga."
784,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : qabila banu Salma key afrad ney chah ke apni mojud rihaaish tarak kar key masjid key qarib muntaqil ho jaeyn. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye baat achchhi na lagi ke wo Madina key ateraaf ko khaali chhod den, isliye aap ney farmaya : aey banu Salma ! kya tumhen apney qadmon sey sawab ki ummid nahin? chunanche wo log (wahin) iqaamat pazeer rahey."
785,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : ansaar (mein sey baaz hazraat) key ghar masjid sey door they. unhoney qarib aana chaha to ye aayat nazil ho gaee : (وَنَكْتُبُ مَا قَدَّمُوا وَآثَارَهُمْ), ''jo kuchh unhoney aagey bheja, hum wo bhi likh letey hain aur unkey nishaanaat bhi likhtey hain.'' chunanche wo log (wahin) thehrey rahey."
786,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi ki jamaat key sath padhi hui namaz uskey ghar ya bazar mein padhi hui namaz sey bees sey ziyada darjey afzal hai."
787,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : namaz ba-jamaat tum mein sey kisi akeley ki namaz sey pachchees hissey afzal hai."
788,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi ka jamaat key sath namaz padhna , ghar mein namaz padhney sey pachchees darjey ziyada (ajr aur sawab ka baais) hai."
789,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi ka jamaat key sath namaz padhna , aadmi key akeley namaz padhney sey sattaais darjey ziyada fazilat rakhta hai."
790,"Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi ka jamaat sey namaz padhna , aadmi key akeley namaz padhney sey chobis ya pachchees darjey ziyada (sawab ka baais) hota hai."
791,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey irada kiya tha ke namaz ki iqaamat kehalwaun, phir kisi aadmi ko hukm dun ke wo logon ko namaz padhaaey, phir jo log namaz mein hazir nahin hotey, unkey paas kuchh mardon ko lakdi key gathon key sath ley jaun aur un (peechhey reh janey walon) key gharon samet aag sey jala dun."
792,"Hazrat ibne Umme Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey arz kiya : main boodha aur na-bina hun, mera ghar door hai aur koi meri marzi key mutabiq mujhey (masjid mein) laney wala nahin, to kya mujhey (jamaat key baghair ghar mein namaz padhney ki) ijazat mil sakti hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum Azan suntey ho? mainey kaha : ji haan, farmaya : tum ko (namaz ba-jamaat sey peechhey rehney ki) koi ijazat nahin."
793,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Azan sun kar (namaz key liye masjid mein) nahin aata , uski koi namaz nahin, siwaye kisi uzr ki surat key."
794,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas aur Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhum sey riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko member par ye farmatey suna : logon ko jamaat tarak karney sey baaz aa jana chahiye, warna Allah Taala unkey dilon par zarur mohar laga dega , phir wo zarur ghaafilon mein shamil ho jaeyngey."
795,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : logon ko chahiye ke jamaat tarak karney sey baaz aa jaeyn warna main zarur unkey gharon ko aag laga dunga."
796,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar logon ko malum ho jaey ke Isha ki namaz aur Fajr ki namaz mein kya kuchh hai. to wo zarur un dono namazon mein hazir hon, chahey unhen ghisat'tey huye aana padey."
797,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : munafiqon par jo namazein sab sey bhari hain, wo Isha ki namaz aur Fajr ki namaz hai, aur agar unhen malum hota ke un mein kya kuchh hai, to wo zarur hazir hotey, chahey ghisat kar aana padta."
798,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they. jo shakhs kisi masjid mein chaalis raat (musalsal) ba-jamaat namaz ada kerey. uski namaz Isha ki pehli rakat (jamaat sey) na chhotey, Allah Taala is amal ki wajeh sey uskey liye jahannam sey azadi likh deta hai."
799,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi (musalman) jab masjid mein dakhil hota hai to jab tak wo namaz ki wajeh sey rukaa huwa hai, wo (sawab key lihaz sey) namaz hi mein (shumar) hota hai. aur (namaz key baad) jab tak wo us jagah betha rehta hai jahan usney namaz padhi, tab tak farishtey uskey haq mein duaayen kartey rehtey hain. kehtey hain : aey Allah ! uski maghfirat farma, aey Allah ! is par reham farma , aey Allah ! uski tauba qubul farma. (us ko ye duayen milti rehti hain) jab tak wahan uska wuzu na toot jaey aur jab tak wo us jagah kisi ko takleef na dey."
800,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo musalman mard namaz aur zikr key liye masjidon mein pabandi sey hazir hota hai, Allah Taala us sey aisa khush hota hai, jis tarah musafir key ghar waley uskey ghar aaney par khush hotey hain."
801,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath maghrib ki namaz ada ki. uskey baad jisey wapis jana tha, wapis chala gaya, aur jaisey bethna tha wo betha raha. (itney mein) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tezi sey tashrif laye, aap ka saans phulaa huwa tha, aur aap ney ghutnon sey kapda utha rakha tha. aap ney farmaya : khush ho jao, tumharey Rab ney aasman ka eik darwaza khola hai aur farishton key samney tumhara zikr fakhr sey kar raha hai, farma raha hai : merey bandon ko dekho, unhoney eik farz ada kiya hai, aur doosrey farz (ki adaegi key waqt) ka intizar kar rahey hain."
802,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum kisi ko masjidon mein jatey dekho to uskey eman ki gawahi do. Allah Taala ney farmaya : ( اِنَّمَا يَعْمُرُ مَسٰجِدَ اللّٰهِ مَنْ اٰمَنَ بِاللّٰهِ), ''Allah ki masjidon ko wohi abad karta hai jo Allah par eman rakhta hai.''"
